  (sub) tree.

  Set ExpandOnNewItem to True if the sub tree the new item belongs to should be expanded to make the
  new item visible.

  Set ExpandOnNewItem to False if adding items should not neccessarily make them visible when one of
  its parents is still collapsed.
See Also
