  ARect   - Rectangle in which to draw the item in. On entry it is assumed to be initialized properly
             (including any indentation for sub items). On exit this will be set to the textual part of
             the item.
  Index   - Index into the items array of the item to render.
  State   - Draw states to consider during drawing. This might be needed to determine which image list
