@@IJvDataItemText
Summary
  Data Item support interface for retrieving the item's textual representation.
Description
  IJvDataItemText is a supporting interface for IJvDataItem that adds the capability of linking a
  caption for an item.

  Almost every provider support the IJvDataItemText interface for its items. Besides access to the
  caption, the interface also keeps track of the editability of the caption from the user interface.
See Also
  IJvDataItem

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@IJvDataItemText.Caption
Summary
  Specifies the caption of the data item.
Description
  Caption specifies the caption for the data item. The caption might be fixed by the object (i.e. it
  can't be changed by assigning a new value to Caption) and might be depending on the current context,
  consumer setting and/or consumer attributes.
See Also
  IJvDataItemText.Editable, IJvDataItemText.GetCaption, IJvDataItemText.SetCaption

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@IJvDataItemText.Editable
Summary
  Specifies if the caption of the item is editable.
Description
  Editable specifies if the caption of the item is editable in the user interface (e.g. an edit
  control). If the caption should be editable from the user interface the method returns True,
  otherwise False is returned.

  Note that the return value of Editable does not neccessarily mean the caption can or can't be
  changed. It only enables/disables the editing from the user interface, but consumers may ignore this
  method if they wish.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@IJvDataItemText.GetCaption
Summary
  Retrieves the caption of the data item.
Description
  GetCaption retrieves the caption of the data item. It's the read access method for the Caption
  property.
See Also
  IJvDataItemText.Caption, IJvDataItemText.SetCaption

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@IJvDataItemText.SetCaption
Summary
  Sets a new caption for the data item.
Description
  SetCaption sets a new caption for the data item. It's the write access method for the Caption
  property.
Parameters
  Value - New caption for the data item.
See Also
